//INFO GAME RULES
ROUND 1-5\nThere are 4 variants of the answer. The user can bet the selected amount of money up to 3 variants. ROUND 6-8\nThere are 3 variants of the answer. The user can bet the selected amount of money up to 2 variants. ROUND 9-10\nThere are 2 variants of the answer. The user can bet the selected amount of money up to 1 variant.
You must place all available money in each round To place money on the chosen variant, complete the shift gesture starting from the pool of money and ending with the selected trapdoor. At the moment you make a mistake, click on the chosen trapdoor, and all the bets will return to the pot. The game requires an internet connection!\nThe - Disable ads - function disables ad serving until the application is restarted.
GOOD LUCK!
